# ICE Crawler AGNT Plugin

Triadic zero-trace repository ingestion for AGNT.

## Quick Start

```bash
npm install
node ice-crawler.js ingest https://github.com/owner/repo
```

## Dashboard

```bash
node ice-crawler.js dashboard 8765
# Open http://localhost:8765
```

## AGNT Plugin

Install the `.agnt` file into AGNT via the plugin manager.

